The paper discusses the design and analysis of multi-agent systems for crisis response, which involves the use of software agents and robots. This falls under the categories of multi-agent systems (cs.MA), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and crisis response (cs.CR).
